e8d629cd-5eeb-46f9-8640-f14b16c43991.question: What are the top 5 industries in terms of revenue?
e8d629cd-5eeb-46f9-8640-f14b16c43991.sql:
SELECT 
  ZI_ES_INDUSTRY AS industry,
  SUM(ZI_C_REVENUE) AS total_revenue
FROM sl-test-project-363109.zoominfo.`zi-retail-companies-headquartered-california`
GROUP BY 
  industry
ORDER BY 
  total_revenue DESC
LIMIT 5;

50dac3e6-46a6-4a9b-bce3-38a7d28309b7.question: What are the top 5 industries in terms of revenue?
50dac3e6-46a6-4a9b-bce3-38a7d28309b7.sql:
SELECT 
  ZI_ES_INDUSTRY AS industry,
  SUM(ZI_C_REVENUE) AS total_revenue
FROM sl-test-project-363109.zoominfo.`zi-retail-companies-headquartered-california`

  industry
